a2t.text_actual: SeoulBus provides you with Korea capital region(Seoul, Incheon and Gyeonggi-do) bus and bus stop information. * Real-time bus arrival information * Bus route information with real-time bus location * Nearby Stop & Bus stop map :: SeoulBus Pro ::  SeoulBus Pro provides you with more advanced features of Seoul Bus, and is available through an auto-renewing subscription.  ◦ Homescreen Widget Add a widget to your homescreen and check bus arrival information by clicking widget. ◦ Dashboard  Dashboard allows you to check up to 6 arrival information right on the front screen.  ◦ Schedule Arrival Alarm  Receive push notification with arrival information at specific day and time you want.
